title: Piranha - remake of the original 1978 Roger Corman cult fave.
description:
Movie Description
A school of genetically altered, flesh-eating piranhas are accidentally released into the wild. They must be stopped before they can spawn and threaten the unsuspecting residents of Lost River Lake. A technologically advanced remake of the original 1978 Roger Corman cult fave.

Credits 
Cast: Alexandra Paul, Soleil Moon Frye, William Katt 
Director: Scott Levy 
Producer: Mike Elliott
